title: LIANE, JUNGLE GODDESS video & audio upgrade

sources.title: LianeJungleGoddessVideoAudioUpgrade
sources.description: This print is significantly sharper than the existing IA copy. Also, the audio is in sync. A jungle girl adventure produced in West Germany. It became a US grindhouse hit in the early '60s because of Marion Michael's nudity Directed by Edvard von Borsody German release 1956 US release 1959 dubbed English complete print a.k.a. "Liane, das Madchen aus dem Urwald"
